OL,3,CHealth Secretary announces he will
OL,4,Cstand down at next year's election
OL,6,FThe Health Secretary, Jeremy Miles MS,
OL,7,Fhas announced he will not be standing
OL,8,Ffor re-election next year.
OL,10,FThe politician, who has represented
OL,11,Fthe Neath constituency for nearly ten
OL,12,Fyears, wrote to the First Minister to
OL,13,Fexplain his decision.
OL,15,FIn the letter to Eluned Morgan, Mr
OL,16,FMiles explained that on "reflection"
OL,17,Fhe has decided it is time to find a
OL,18,Fnew challenge and so will not run as a
OL,19,Fcandidate next May.
