OL,3,CHealth Secretary announces he will
OL,4,Cstand down at next year's election
OL,6,FHe said: "Upon reflection this summer,
OL,7,FI decided that the end of this Senedd
OL,8,Fterm is the time for me to seek a new
OL,9,Fand different challenge, one which
OL,10,Fallows me perhaps to strike a better
OL,11,Fbalance between work and those in my
OL,12,Flife who I love."
OL,14,FHe also thanked Ms Morgan for the
OL,15,F"trust she had shown" in appointing
OL,16,Fhim as Health Secretary.
