OL,3,CHealth Secretary announces he will
OL,4,Cstand down at next year's election
OL,6,FHe added: "The health and social care
OL,7,Fworkforce are a daily inspiration to
OL,8,Fme. I will continue to devote every
OL,9,Fday I have left in the role to
OL,10,Fbuilding on the progress we are
OL,11,Falready seeing in reducing waiting
OL,12,Ftimes and improving health and care
OL,13,Fservices - the priorities you have set
OL,14,Fout.
OL,16,F"I joined the Cabinet the year after I
OL,17,Fwas first given the immense honour of
OL,18,Fbeing elected to the Senedd to
OL,19,Frepresent the communities of Neath
OL,20,Fconstituency, almost a decade ago.
