OL,3,CHealth Secretary announces he will
OL,4,Cstand down at next year's election
OL,6,F"It has been a privilege, and I have
OL,7,Fworked with many wonderful people, to
OL,8,Fwhom I am endlessly thankful. As you
OL,9,Fwill know, being in frontline politics
OL,10,Fis all-consuming and takes precedence
OL,11,Fover so much else in life. The
OL,12,Fpressure is real and sustained over a
OL,13,Flong period."
OL,15,FMr Miles was appointed as Cabinet
OL,16,FSecretary for Health and Social Care
OL,17,Fin September 2024 but has also
OL,18,Fpreviously had responsibility for the
OL,19,FEconomy, Energy and Welsh Language
OL,20,Fbrief and was Brexit Minister.
